txt.en: 'Follow Bilbo's trail into the Misty Mountains, my persistent friend. And stay alert as you go, for those paths are dangerous, especially in winter. It may be that Kúblugat is not the only spirit of the storm haunting those slopes!\n\n'Good fortune go with you, and bring Bilbo unharmed back to us!'

'It is clear from the words of Glóin that Bilbo's trail must lead into the Misty Mountains. But where is he going, and why?\n\n'Are you still resolved to follow him? Tell me that you are, [placeholder]!'
05. The Further Adventures of Bilbo Baggins, Chapter 5
You may be ambushed after completing your objective.
There is no shortage of adventure out there for a curious and wandering hobbit. What has Bilbo Baggins gotten up to now?
Complete 'Mission: The Further Adventures of Bilbo Baggins, Chapter 5'
Your mission is to find Bilbo Baggins. Speak to Celeblír to continue the search!
Celeblír is west of the Last Homely House, near the Town Crier.
'This is terrible! Bilbo has been captured by goblins? Again?'
